{"id":5345,"date":"2012-08-19T05:40:51","date_gmt":"2012-08-19T01:40:51","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=5345"},"modified":"2023-10-05T21:45:42","modified_gmt":"2023-10-05T17:45:42","slug":"allah-only-merciful","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/19\/allah-only-merciful\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Rahmah: Allah is only merciful to the merciful"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Usamah ibn Zayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, &#8220;<strong>Verily,\u00a0Allah is merciful only to His servants who are merciful.<\/strong>&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7448, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 923<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0<\/em><\/strong>(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e<\/span> <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627<\/s